events.name: (almost still) June Meetup
events.description: Hello Container Geeks, DockerCon 2016 is on from 19th to 21st of June in Seattle, so Vincent De Smet is going to give us a recap. You can also expect some exciting announcements! We are still looking for other speakers, drop us a message if you have anything you'd like to share! Any contributions from beginner to expert are most welcome! RSVPs will be opened 10 days ahead of the event, so stay tuned! Update: Soedarsono will share his experience doing Ruby development using Docker! [Edit] - Due to location availability we have to move the meetup to July 4th at HonestBee. We're sorry for any inconvenience. Still looking forward to see you soon, The Docker SG team
events.location: Honestbee, #04-01B Delta House, 2 Alexandra Road, 159919, Singapore
